# Project icon assets. Some machines have a global `Icon` ignore pattern for
# macOS custom folder icons; keep the real asset directory visible to git.
!assets/icon/
!assets/icon/**
assets/icon/**/.DS_Store
assets/icon/**/.goutputstream-*
assets/icon/macos/*.iconset/

# macOS
**/.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon?
._*
